node.text:
This week, we’re eating the meals from our favorite movie scenes. Play
along with me: Share a photo of your order inspired by a BINGO square. Tag @sanpellegrino_us, #promotion, #supportrestaurants. Together, we can support our local restaurants, and for every image shared, S.Pellegrino will donate $1 to the @beardfoundation Food and Beverage Investment Fund for Black and Indigenous Americans, up to $50,000.00. Let’s eat!

node.text: Two more weeks of Restaurant Bingo! Are you ready to eat to the tune of the ABCs? T is for Tofu. A is for Avocado Toast. N is for National Chili Day... I know what I’ll be ordering this week to #supportrestaurants! Play along with me: Share a photo of your order inspired by a BINGO square. Tag @sanpellegrino_us, #promotion, #supportrestaurants. AND, not only will we help local restaurants, but S.Pellegrino will also donate $1 to the @beardfoundation Food and Beverage Investment Fund for Black and Indigenous Americans, up to $50,000.00. Have fun!

“Around the World!” My friends at @sanpellegrino_us and I would love for you to play along to #SupportRestaurants. How? Just share a photo of the meal you order that’s inspired by a BINGO square (tag @sanpellegrino_us, #promotion, #supportrestaurants), and S.Pellegrino will donate $1 to the @beardfoundation Food and Beverage Investment Fund for Black and Indigenous Americans, up to $50,000.00. Let’s eat!

node.text:
Welcome to Restaurant BINGO, brought to you by @sanpellegrino_us. I’m thrilled to bring you this game... where we eat to #SupportRestaurants. Each Friday for the next four weeks, I’ll be sharing a BINGO board full of fun restaurant order challenges. The more we order, the more we get to support our favorite local restaurants. AND, for each BINGO square played, S.Pellegrino will
donate $1 to the @beardfoundation Food and Beverage Investment Fund for Black and Indigenous Americans, up to $50,000.00 over the four weeks. More info at @sanpellegrino_us  #Ad

node.text: A HUGE congrats to my fellow cast mates/friends, entire crew, scout, ITV America and Netflix on 6 Emmy Nominations for our little show. I don’t have the words to express how grateful I am to the voters, and all of you out there who have supported our show. It means the world to me.  Thank you. Thank you. Thank you. ❤️

node.text:
Final days in Iceland. So sad to leave this most beautiful I’ve ever seen. Before we go….
1. One last pose in those fields of purple flowers
2. Tit soup (blue lagoon) 
3. The best person I know 
4. The most amazing hotel/spa experience ever @retreat.bluelagoon 

Thanks for letting me share all my holiday snaps, like a proper grandpa! 
On to London next, because I’m also “COMING HOME”. 🤗
